ge 3 and primary stages, leveraging their expertise in creating GCSE and A-level materials. This experience positions them well to contribute to lower-level resources by adapting analysis-based learning approaches and utilizing technology.&#10;5. To address concerns about curriculum reform and the introduction of new curriculum, the WJEC is engaging in discussions with relevant stakeholders, including publishers and the Welsh Government, to ensure a smooth transition and maintain resource quality.">
