ntribute to a more diverse range of offerings for Welsh schools.&#10;&#10;In summary, teacher autonomy is important for tailoring curriculum delivery to students' needs, while adjustments to regulations could incentivize Welsh providers like the WJEC to play a larger role in addressing the shortage of resource providers in Wales.">
