bate with the qualifications regulator on this matter.&#10;&#10;In summary, providing a healthier model for education in the future could involve moving away from a strong reliance on textbooks, ensuring independence in state models, or de-emphasizing textbooks altogether. Additionally, it is important to develop resources that support assessment objectives focusing on analysis and evaluation to cater to the shifts in learning goals in various subjects.">
