ch being implemented as an experiment at the request of the Welsh Government. However, they can only work on those books that are in the process of being developed.&#10;4. Hodder Education acknowledges the concern about delaying English versions of textbooks by two months but emphasizes the importance of equitable treatment for both languages. They are open to a chapter-by-chapter approach to mitigate this issue.">
